{"tid":1529882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那話我地過唔到八月十五","createTime":"2019-09-01T23:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:05:16.000Z","uid":242805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3779d16f8b929b7d909e3dde02b16918e3ae1e16","tid":1529882,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />膠膠地<br />\n根據支那國8月15言論<br />\n直頭係想見人就捉，佢地不知幾想我地係咁示威之後捉哂我地<br />\n同時又唔批不反對通知書攞正牌捉<br />\n所以大家要諗諗係咪要由小型傳統遊行變遊擊同埋街坊者示威<br />\n街坊式示威真係好撚勁<br />\n點解我咁講？因為大家共識都想捱到十月一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bab36bc9623a4e4a3fc5c6aa1b1617fc204b57","tid":1529882,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家共識係捱到贏為止"},{"pid":"3272fa0d2cd3bc2fa7dc740371602a6467bc5471","tid":1529882,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"係做到野就而家即刻做啦仲等<br />\n<br />\n同2020取代香港一樣咁on9"}]}